| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0393 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3cc09895-cd65-56af-b4c1-cd2d7fecba6a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
